name: Spacesuit Goddess
description: Indeed, it is a spacesuit. She is the Goddess of Spacesuits. She can bless your rocket and make sure it lands properly. She can also make sure your space walk goes without a hitch. She can do so much, but her focus is on spacesuits. When an astronaut wears a spacesuit, it is blessed by her, whether they know it or not.
